eGap="0" SameSize="true" Type="Newspaper"/><CHAR>최소표면적 문제(catenary problem)</CHAR></TEXT><TEXT CharShape="14"><FOOTNOTE><PARALIST LineWrap="Break" LinkListID="0" LinkListIDNext="0" TextDirection="0" VertAlign="Top"><P ParaShape="3" Style="11"><TEXT CharShape="17"><AUTONUM Number="1" NumberType="Footnote"><AUTONUMFORMAT SuffixChar=")" Superscript="false" Type="Digit"/></AUTONUM><CHAR> 이태리어로 사슬(chain)을 의미하는 ‘catena’에서 유래</CHAR></TEXT></P></PARALIST></FOOTNOTE></TEXT><TEXT CharShape="0"><CHAR/></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="14" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="14"/></P><P ParaShape="5" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="14"><EQUATION BaseLine="72" BaseUnit="1000" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="2110713495" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="34"><SIZE Height="1190" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="7130" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT>수식입니다.</SHAPECOMMENT></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>(x  _{0} ,`y  _{0} ),``(x  _{1} ,`y  _{1} )</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR>를 연결하는 곡선 중 x 축을 중심으로 회전했을 때 최소 표면적을 만드는 곡선을 찾아라. </CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="5" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="14"/></P><P ParaShape="5" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="14"><EQUATION BaseLine="72" BaseUnit="1000" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="2110713496" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="74"><SIZE Height="1190" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="7130" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="