r="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT>수식입니다.</SHAPECOMMENT></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>b-y`=`P(1-cos theta `)`</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR/></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="5" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="14"/></P><P ParaShape="5" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="14"><CHAR>시작점이 (a, b)이므로 y = b를 대입하면 </CHAR><EQUATION BaseLine="86" BaseUnit="1000" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="2110713662" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="130"><SIZE Height="1000" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="2545" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT>수식입니다.</SHAPECOMMENT></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>theta `=`0</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR/></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="5" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="14"/></P><P ParaShape="5" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="14"><CHAR>②에 대입하면 </CHAR><EQUATION BaseLine="86" BaseUnit="1000" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="2110713663" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="131"><SIZE Height="1000" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="9620" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT>수식입니다.</SHAPECOMMENT></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>`a=`P( theta `-`sin theta )+`Q</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR/></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="5" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="14"/></P><P ParaShape="5" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="14"><CHAR>∴ </CHAR><EQUATION BaseLine="86" BaseUnit="1000" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="2110713664" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="132"><SIZE Height="1000" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="2845" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT>수식입니다.</SHAPECOMMENT></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>Q`=`a</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR/></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="5" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="14"/></P><P ParaShape="5" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="14"><CHAR>따라서 시작점이 (a, b)일 때 매개변수방정식은</CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="5" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="14"/></P><P ParaShape="5" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="14"><EQUATION BaseLine="86" BaseUnit="1000" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="2110713665" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="114"><SIZE Height="1000" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="9395" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT>수식입니다.</SHAPECOMMENT></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>`x=`P( theta `-`sin theta )+`a</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR> </CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="5" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="14"><EQUATION BaseLine="86" BaseUnit="1000" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="2110713666" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="115"><SIZE Height="1000" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="10350" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT>수식입니다.</SHAPECOMMENT></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>y`=`-P(1-cos theta `)`+`b</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR> </CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="5" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="14"/></P><P ParaShape="5" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="14"><CHAR>예) A(0, 1)에서 B(1, 0)로 구르는 구슬의 최소시간 궤적을 구하라.</CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="5" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="14"/></P><P ParaShape="5" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="14"><CHAR>(풀이)</CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="5" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="14"><CHAR>A(0, 1)을 대입하면 </CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="5" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="14"/></P><P ParaShape="5" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="14"><EQUATION BaseLine="72" BaseUnit="1000" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="2110713667" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="119"><SIZE Height="1190" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="10675" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT>수식입니다.</SHAPECOMMENT></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>`0=`P( theta   _{A} `-`sin theta   _{A} )+``a</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR>.............① </CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="5" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="14"><EQUATION BaseLine="72" BaseUnit="1000" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="2110713668" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="120"><SIZE Height="1190" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="10700" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT>수식입니다.</SHAPECOMMENT></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>1`=`-P(1-cos theta   _{A} `)+b</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR>..............②</CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="5" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="14"/></P><P ParaShape="5" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="14"><CHAR>B(1, 0)을 대입하면 </CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="5" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="14"/></P><P ParaShape="5" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="14"><EQUATION BaseLine="72" BaseUnit="1000" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="2110713669" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="121"><SIZE Height="1190" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="10525" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT>수식입니다.</SHAPECOMMENT></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>`1=`P( theta   _{B} `-`sin theta   _{B} )+``a</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR>...............③</CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="5" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="14"><EQUATION BaseLine="71" BaseUnit="1000" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="2110713670" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="122"><SIZE Height="1202" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="10655" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT>수식입니다.</SHAPECOMMENT></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>0`=`-P(1-cos theta `  _{B} )+b</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR>...............④</CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="5" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="14"/></P><P ParaShape="5" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="14"><CHAR>시작점 A(0, 1)이므로 a = 0, b = 1,</CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="5" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="14"/></P><P ParaShape="5" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="14"><CHAR>①, ②에서 </CHAR><EQUATION BaseLine="72" BaseUnit="1000" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="2110713671" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="125"><SIZE Height="1190" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="3145" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT>수식입니다.</SHAPECOMMENT></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>theta   _{A} `=`0</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR/></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="5" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="14"/></P><P ParaShape="5" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="14"><CHAR>③, ④는 </CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="5" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="14"/></P><P ParaShape="5" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="14"><EQUATION BaseLine="72" BaseUnit="1000" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="2110713672" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="135"><SIZE Height="1190" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="8645" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT>수식입니다.</SHAPECOMMENT></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>`1=`P( theta   _{B} `-`sin theta   _{B} )</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR/></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="5" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="14"><EQUATION BaseLine="71" BaseUnit="1000" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="2110713673" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="136"><SIZE Heig